Blacknightmare::

She smiled to Orchestra and said "And you're the nicest male that 
I've seen in my life"

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "dcoburn" <dcoburn@n...> wrote:
> ::Orchestra/Symphony::
> 
>       Orchestra laughed one last time.
> 
>        "Heh, I can see us rising now!!  HAHAHA!" He cackled.
> 
>         THen, he paused and looked at Blacknightmare.
> 
>          "You know, if you don't mind me saying, you're kindof 
attractive,"
> He said, he would be blushing if transformers could blush.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
>          Symphony was worried as Kluster went into battle.  
Symphony was not
> used to going into battle, and therefore had always been separate 
from his
> brothers Composer and Orchestra as they went into wars long ago.  
Composer
> was a top strategist and even lead squads sometimes.  Orchestra was 
a
> stealthy covert ops agent, always uncovering even the most hidden
> information.  But Symphony had yet to find any skill in himself.  
But he had
> to prove he had some fighting strength!  He wouldn't let his 
peaceful ways
> get in the way of being accepted into a war faction.
> 
>         "Here I come!!!" He yelled, running after Kluster into the 
battle.
> 
>          Symphony pulled out his machine gun and fired 22 shots at 
Kluster's
> target, Reflector.
